---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Work">
  <h1>Our Work</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    We work at the intersection of research, operational insight, and system design — helping institutions deliver
    better outcomes with measurable impact.
  </p>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card">
      <h2>Research &amp; Systems Evaluation</h2>
      <p>
        Evidence-led assessment of institutional performance, service delivery, community needs, and operational bottlenecks.
        We translate findings into clear recommendations and measurable improvement plans.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Service evaluation &amp; needs assessment</li>
        <li>Baseline measurement and KPI design</li>
        <li>Cost-efficiency and process mapping</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Innovation &amp; Pilot Programmes</h2>
      <p>
        Design and testing of scalable models in controlled community environments. Pilots are built to produce evidence
        for responsible scale — not assumptions.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Feasibility studies and partnership mapping</li>
        <li>Pilot delivery with defined KPIs</li>
        <li>Evaluation and scalability assessment</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="link" href="/innovation">Explore innovation →</a>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Advisory &amp; Capacity Building</h2>
      <p>
        Workshops, training, and strategic support to strengthen organisations. We focus on building internal capability,
        governance clarity, and sustainable implementation.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Training, workshops and facilitation</li>
        <li>Operational improvement and change support</li>
        <li>Impact measurement and reporting</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="link" href="/contact">Partner with us →</a>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="bar">
    <div>
      <h3>How we work</h3>
      <p>
        We start small, measure rigorously, and scale responsibly: <strong>Pilot → Measure → Refine → Scale</strong>.
        This approach supports credible funding, strong delivery, and long-term sustainability.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/projects">View projects</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/governance">Governance</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 40px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 90ch;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      align-items: start;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .card ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-weight: 850;
      color: rgba(39, 99, 235, 0.95);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .bar {
      margin-top: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(39, 99, 235, 0.06), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.06));
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .bar h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .bar p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 80ch;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: white;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .btn.primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(39, 99, 235, 0.10), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.10));
      border-color: rgba(39, 99, 235, 0.25);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .bar {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
